snippet.title: Shy Cats Hidden Tracks - Paris // Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/2834400/Shy_Cats_Hidden_Tracks__Paris/
 
A unique musical hidden object game where you search the streets of Paris for singing kittens from a choir and money bags to hire and assemble a cat band. As orchestra conductor, you'll be able to configure the musicians as you wish, creating your own music and choir melodies. Find them all!

Developed by 
@enchantgames_
